metadata.name: Open Eggition
metadata.description:
An egg that's so famous, a true viral gem,  
Inspiring NFTs that now rule the trend,  
With a price of 0.0000069e, it's not much,  
But the story of this egg is worth a touch.

Burning and scrambling, new ways to play,  
With NFTs, you can now do it every day,  
Just like the instagram egg that made a mark,  
30 million likes in just 10 days, it's quite the feat, it's quite the spark.

So let's aim for 30 million mints in 10 days,  
A new record set, a new goal in the race,  
Inspired by the egg, it's open edition style,  
A new way to collect, a new way to smile.

So join in the fun, and don't be left behind,  
With NFTs, you too can be a collector of the kind.
